  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl06_LabelType\">Having grown up near the Worldwound, you have a rough understanding of the demons&rsquo; guttural babble.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl06_LabelType\">Sarkoris or the Worldwound</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl06_LabelType\">You add Abyssal to your list of languages known, though you take a &ndash;2 penalty on Diplomacy, Intimidate, and Bluff checks made while speaking Abyssal, as well as a &ndash;2 penalty on Linguistics checks made to read Abyssal text. If you gain Abyssal as a language again at a later time (such as by taking a rank in Linguistics and selecting Abyssal as a learned language), these skill check penalties become +2 trait bonuses instead.</span></p>",
